        "TileImage": "$($repository 3880a7bb-7b59-4a0c-87f2-590e87ccb1ce).Image",
        "Description": "LOCATION: Whittleton Creek.\rTARGETS: Helen West and associates, Charles Blake III.\r\rThis seemingly idyllic suburbia conceals converging threats. Helen West runs a bakery front linked to disappearances; evidence indicates her staff knowingly assist in procurement and processing of human remains as ingredients. Charles Blake III, long-time HOA chairman turned candidate, enforces arbitrary rules through intimidation and coercion. The client requires all targets eliminated. Discretion is paramount.",
